MAPPING.DESCRIPTION: This mapping loads the Current Year DTC Return Scrapped data into the Gorssmargin table.
MAPPING.NAME: m_GM_DTC_RET_SCRAP

TRANSFORMATION.DESCRIPTION: Look up transformation to get the specific Item_ids from the table slba_item.This is the main look up for getting Item_Id. If this look up returns null values then the LKP_SLBA_ITEM_NS values will be used.
TRANSFORMATION.NAME: LKP_SLBA_ITEM

TABLEATTRIBUTE.NAME: Lookup Sql Override
TABLEATTRIBUTE.VALUE: SELECT SLBA_ITEM.ITEM_ID as ITEM_ID, SLBA_ITEM.GARM_PER_PKG_QTY as GARM_PER_PKG_QTY, LTRIM(RTRIM(SLBA_ITEM.STYLE_NUM)) as STYLE_NUM, LTRIM(RTRIM(SLBA_ITEM.COLOR_CODE)) as COLOR_CODE, LTRIM(RTRIM(SLBA_ITEM.SIZE_DESC)) as SIZE_DESC, SLBA_ITEM.DIVISION_CODE as DIVISION_CODE FROM SLBA_ITEM WHERE SLBA_ITEM.DIVISION_CODE='DR'

TABLEATTRIBUTE.NAME: Lookup condition
TABLEATTRIBUTE.VALUE: STYLE_NUM = I_STYLE_NUM AND COLOR_CODE = I_COLOR_CODE AND SIZE_DESC = I_SIZE_DESC AND DIVISION_CODE = I_DIVISION_CODE

TRANSFORMATION.DESCRIPTION: Source qualifier reads the records from the source and it supplies two hard coded values for the look up transformations to get the exact item id. DR and DR-NS are the hardcoded fileds
TRANSFORMATION.NAME: SQ_TRETCY

TRANSFORMATION.DESCRIPTION: Lookup transformation to get the fiscal_year and fiscl_period.
TRANSFORMATION.NAME: LKP_DAY_DIM

TABLEATTRIBUTE.NAME: Lookup Sql Override
TABLEATTRIBUTE.VALUE: SELECT DAY_DIMENSION.AS_OF_DATE as AS_OF_DATE, DAY_DIMENSION.CY_MONTH_NUM as CY_MONTH_NUM, DAY_DIMENSION.CY_YEAR_YYYY as CY_YEAR_YYYY, DAY_DIMENSION.CY_WK_OF_YEAR as CY_WK_OF_YEAR, DAY_DIMENSION.DAY_DATE as DAY_DATE FROM day_dimension where DAY_DIMENSION.DAY_DATE = trunc(to_date(sysdate)-7)

TRANSFORMATION.DESCRIPTION: expresion to convert the date data type
TRANSFORMATION.NAME: EXP_CONVERSION

TRANSFORMATION.DESCRIPTION: Lookup on the table slba_facility to get the Facility Id's
TRANSFORMATION.NAME: LKP_SLBA_FACILITY

TABLEATTRIBUTE.NAME: Lookup Sql Override
TABLEATTRIBUTE.VALUE: SELECT SLBA_FACILITY.FACILITY_ID as FACILITY_ID, SLBA_FACILITY.DIVISION_GROUP as DIVISION_GROUP, SLBA_FACILITY.FACILITY_CODE as FACILITY_CODE FROM SLBA_FACILITY WHERE SLBA_FACILITY.DIVISION_GROUP = 'sld' AND SLBA_FACILITY.FACILITY_CODE = '--'

TRANSFORMATION.DESCRIPTION: Look up on the table slba_customer_xref to get the customer id's
TRANSFORMATION.NAME: LKP_SLBA_CUSTOMER_XREF

TRANSFORMATION.DESCRIPTION: Filter outs the records with null values.
TRANSFORMATION.NAME: FIL_DAY_DIM

TABLEATTRIBUTE.NAME: Filter Condition
TABLEATTRIBUTE.VALUE: NOT ISNULL(CY_MONTH_NUM) AND NOT ISNULL(CY_YEAR_YYYY) AND NOT ISNULL(CY_WK_OF_YEAR)

TRANSFORMATION.DESCRIPTION: Look up transformatoin to read the 'Non specific' item_ids from the table slba_item. The style_num 'DR-NS' is the hardcoded input from the source qualifier. This look up also reurns the garm_perpkg_qty.
TRANSFORMATION.NAME: LKP_SLBA_ITEM_NS

TABLEATTRIBUTE.NAME: Lookup Sql Override
TABLEATTRIBUTE.VALUE: SELECT SLBA_ITEM.ITEM_ID as ITEM_ID, SLBA_ITEM.GARM_PER_PKG_QTY as GARM_PER_PKG_QTY, SLBA_ITEM.STYLE_NUM as STYLE_NUM FROM SLBA_ITEM WHERE SLBA_ITEM.STYLE_NUM = 'DR-NS'

TRANSFORMATION.DESCRIPTION: Aggregate the records using the key fileds and summarize Garment, Dozens and Units
TRANSFORMATION.NAME: AGG_GM

TABLEATTRIBUTE.NAME: Lookup Sql Override
TABLEATTRIBUTE.VALUE: SELECT Reference.Desc_2 as Desc_2, Reference.Reference_sub_key_2 as Reference_sub_key_2, Reference.Desc_1 as Desc_1 FROM ( select LTRIM(RTRIM(Reference.Desc_1)) as Desc_1, LTRIM(RTRIM(Reference.Reference_sub_key_2)) as Reference_sub_key_2, LTRIM(RTRIM(Reference.Desc_2)) as Desc_2 from dbo.reference Reference with(nolock) where REFERENCE_KEY ='DTC_ONEWORLD_Mapping' and reference_sub_key_1='Sold_to' ) Reference

TRANSFORMATION.DESCRIPTION: Expression transformation to perform arithmetic and logical operations on the records. Also performs the hardcoding of default values.

SESSION.DESCRIPTION: This session runs the mapping m_GROSS_MARGIN_DTC_RET_SCRAP and loads records to target
SESSION.NAME: s_m_GM_DTC_RET_SCRAP_CY

ATTRIBUTE.NAME: Sql Query
ATTRIBUTE.VALUE: SELECT PROD_LINE, PRODUCT_CATEGORY, INV_MGMT_BRAND_CD, RET_REASON_GRP, RET_REASON_CD, WEEK_ENDING_DT, FISCAL_YR, FISCAL_MTH, LTRIM(RTRIM(STYLE)) STYLE, LTRIM(RTRIM(SZ)) SZ, LTRIM(RTRIM(COLOR)) COLOR, UNITS_RETURNED, UNITS_REPLACED, UNITS_REPKGED, UNITS_RET_TO_STOCK, UNITS_SCRAPPED, 'DR', 'DR-NS' FROM PMC.TRETCY@GANYMEDE.slci.net WHERE UNITS_SCRAPPED>0

ATTRIBUTE.NAME: Lookup Sql Override
ATTRIBUTE.VALUE: SELECT DAY_DIMENSION.AS_OF_DATE as AS_OF_DATE, DAY_DIMENSION.CY_MONTH_NUM as CY_MONTH_NUM, DAY_DIMENSION.CY_YEAR_YYYY as CY_YEAR_YYYY, DAY_DIMENSION.CY_WK_OF_YEAR as CY_WK_OF_YEAR, DAY_DIMENSION.DAY_DATE as DAY_DATE FROM DAY_DIMENSION where DAY_DIMENSION.DAY_DATE = trunc(to_date(sysdate)-7)
